name: Music for Your Soul Tshirt
description:
Music for your soul was designed as a tribute to all the music lovers out there. It reminds us about the importance of music and how it can affect our mood or life in a positive way. Let the music touch your soul with music for your soul by Toni Payne. This wonderful design depicts a microphone with musical notes dancing round it.

	Comes in an ultra soft high end poly cotton blend Tshirt

name: I am Haute Green Tshirt
description: I am Haute Positee signifies being a hot fashionista in a high end way. You are not just hot, you are high end, high class hotness.

name: Akanke Faceless Beauty Tshirt
description:
Akanke Faceless beauty is drawn from the idea of a special lady/girl. Akanke translates to a female that is to be adored, this person is someone that is to be cherished and treated like a rare gem. The design remaining faceless represents you, me, and everyone else that considers themselves special. It could be your mother, sister, friend, or girlfriend.  If you consider a female in your life special, Akanke faceless beauty is a great way of telling them.

	Comes in a soft poly cotton blend Style
